s that we\nneed to accommodate fast flavor conversions in realistic CCSN models.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 16 Aug 2021 18:00:04 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 24 Aug 2021 04:07:41 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-11-03"}
