 of modulation instability provides\na powerful tool for Kerr optical frequency-comb generation via pump modulation\nand cavity detuning tuning scheme in dual-coupled cavities.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 17 Aug 2021 04:43:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-02-09"}
