 on instances from PACE\n2017 and other sources show that this implementation is extremely fast and\neffective for graphs of practical interest.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 17 Aug 2021 10:38:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-08-18"}
