 a new leading benchmark for both\nfully- and weakly-supervised panoptic segmentation. Our code and models are\nmade publicly available at https://github.com/dvlab-research/PanopticFCN.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 17 Aug 2021 15:28:53 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 18 Aug 2021 02:15:32 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 13 Oct 2022 03:42:27 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-10-14"}
